verbose_text: A negative correlation was identified between miR-126 with cTN-I (R 2 = 0.6758; XREF_FIG) and NT-pro-BNP (R 2 = 0.8317; XREF_FIG) levels whereas a positive correlation between miR-21 with cTN-I level (R 2 = 0.7066; XREF_FIG) and NT-pro-BNP level (R 2 = 8601; XREF_FIG) among atherosclerotic patients (XREF_FIG) was observed.
